{"tid":2260633,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"香港能量點","createTime":"2020-10-27T17:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T15:34:45.000Z","uid":102640,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"46062b3bf3712740747980040c4b98d1b0ad5270","tid":2260633,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T17:20:04.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇喺外地或者香港有去過一啲能量點呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E9%BB%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%25BB%259E&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDLeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=798fa298\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%83%BD%E9%87%8F%E9%BB%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n例如我去過日本鞍馬山（網上好多討論都認為鞍馬山係京都其中一個能量點）<br />\n雖然我自己冇乜特別感應，但嗰度嘅景色同空氣的確令人感覺舒服。同埋嗰度有幾間歴史悠久嘅神社，其中一間重有一棵九百年嘅神樹。山入面其他大樹都有過百年歷史，完全想像到入夜嗰時會變千與千尋。<br />\n<br />\n反觀香港又冇乜人特別提過邊度係香港嘅能量點？<br />\n有冇師兄分享吓？"},{"pid":"2defa9939c0e01e8fd03a05a133741fb9ad95fa9","tid":2260633,"uid":181014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"留名 好信能量呢樣野 <br />\n之前去過西貢個昂坪山頂 感覺到個到幾有能量下"},{"pid":"9c339225c94b94bc2c34239611f74020a1c6889a","tid":2260633,"uid":48286,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T17:31:56.000Z","msg":"富士山總面積約為900平方公里<br />\n琵琶湖面積670平方公里<br />\n香港面積1106平方公里<br />\n<br />\n香港本身就係一個能量點"},{"pid":"3c9a19048d86e1d57ff7409b0404efd25fb865c2","tid":2260633,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"香港個能量點喺淺水灣"},{"pid":"5c1580b1eaeb29fa963e2126df8d75f76a1b9169","tid":2260633,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2defa9939c0e01e8fd03a05a133741fb9ad95fa9","tid":2260633,"uid":181014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"留名 好信能量呢樣野 <br />\n之前去過西貢個昂坪山頂 感覺到個到幾有能量下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T18:50:56.000Z","msg":"即係昂坪草地？<br />\n我都想去吓，嗰度幾靚。"},{"pid":"994bd29ae0f47811d4734ac729292280c246a904","tid":2260633,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9a19048d86e1d57ff7409b0404efd25fb865c2","tid":2260633,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T17:56:01.000Z","msg":"香港個能量點喺淺水灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T18:51:23.000Z","msg":"可唔可以分享多啲？"},{"pid":"06d2347f63371fe7d68828c03b4925269fbf0020","tid":2260633,"uid":235001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:44:04.000Z","msg":"睇錯左做馬鞍山"},{"pid":"655e575e7bc144a06de5de26b4a7839686bf60fc","tid":2260633,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06d2347f63371fe7d68828c03b4925269fbf0020","tid":2260633,"uid":235001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T09:44:04.000Z","msg":"睇錯左做馬鞍山"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T19:06:11.000Z","msg":"正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060d50dee0546d92be1075aa015e4f8e93d0dbfe","tid":2260633,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"我去過高街鬼屋，已經拆得7788。但經過未拆嘅外牆時候（同埋我有摸到），feel 到突然其來嘅不自在，應該有好混亂嘅負能量留左喺度<br />\n<br />\n其他體驗過嘅能量點仲有香港大學（正面能量）、大嶼山（自然能量）&hellip;"},{"pid":"856398a4323be10c0616367b78539912b4e83ea5","tid":2260633,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"060d50dee0546d92be1075aa015e4f8e93d0dbfe","tid":2260633,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T01:09:19.000Z","msg":"我去過高街鬼屋，已經拆得7788。但經過未拆嘅外牆時候（同埋我有摸到），feel 到突然其來嘅不自在，應該有好混亂嘅負能量留左喺度<br />\n<br />\n其他體驗過嘅能量點仲有香港大學（正面能量）、大嶼山（自然能量）&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"睇嚟你有敏感體質喎<br />\n有冇去過宗教場所或者寺廟？"},{"pid":"b207da3d251e44b45641b943d11c535f2985fa73","tid":2260633,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"856398a4323be10c0616367b78539912b4e83ea5","tid":2260633,"uid":102640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"060d50d